# Problem: ``

This site `https://www.boxentriq.com/code-breaking/cipher-identifier#base64` was really helpful. Click the `Text` options. Or we can use our command line to complete this.

```bash
echo  | rev | base64 -d | base64 -d | xxd -r -p

00000000  3d 3d 51 66 78 45 47 4f 78 51 57 4f 78 6b 44 4f  |==QfxEGOxQWOxkDO|
00000010  7a 51 47 4f 35 51 44 5a 78 67 54 5a 30 67 54 4d  |zQGO5QDZxgTZ0gTM|
00000020  31 49 57 59 6d 46 32 4d 34 63 54 4e 6a 64 7a 65  |1IWYmF2M4cTNjdze|
00000030  47 52 31 51 54 42 31 52                          |GR1QTB1R|
```

Looks like the base64 contents are inverted. Let's change them `R1BTQ1RGezdjNTc4M2FmYWI1MTg0ZTgxZDQ5OGQzODkxOWQxOGExfQ==
`
